"title": "8328: quietness",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8328",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A calm, peaceful and restrained attitude to life and way of approaching God frequently commended in Scripture even in adverse circumstances. It is also a condition experienced by God's friends and enemies when confronted by his majesty.</p>\n<h2>Quietness of life</h2>\n<h3>A quiet manner of life commended</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:1-1Tim2:2\">1TI 2:1–2:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:20\">PSA 35:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps131:1-Ps131:2\">PSA 131:1–131:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:19\">MAT 12:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:2\">ISA 42:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:11\">1TH 4:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:12\">2TH 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:11\">1TI 2:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:1-1Pet3:4\">1PE 3:1–3:4</a></p>\n<h3>A quiet temperament</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen25:27\">GEN 25:27</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Quiet activity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:19\">MAT 1:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg4:21\">JDG 4:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth3:7\">RUT 3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek24:17\">EZK 24:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:37\">ACT 16:37</a></p>\n<h3>The wisdom of being quiet</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:13\">AMO 5:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen34:5\">GEN 34:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg18:19-Judg18:20\">JDG 18:19–18:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth7:4\">EST 7:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:18\">PRO 15:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:17\">ECC 9:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:35-Acts19:36\">ACT 19:35–19:36</a></p>\n<h2>Quietness in different circumstances</h2>\n<h3>In peace and rest</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps23:2\">PSA 23:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr4:40\">1CH 4:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:1\">PRO 17:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa32:17\">ISA 32:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:31\">MRK 6:31</a></p>\n<h3>After conflict</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:9\">1CH 22:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh11:23\">JOS 11:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh14:15\">JOS 14:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:11\">JDG 3:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg5:31\">JDG 5:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg8:28\">JDG 8:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr14:1\">2CH 14:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:30\">2CH 20:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:7\">ISA 14:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer30:10\">JER 30:10</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer46:27\">JER 46:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech1:11\">ZEC 1:11</a></p>\n<h3>When in distress</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam13:20\">2SA 13:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh8:9-Neh8:11\">NEH 8:9–8:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa7:4\">ISA 7:4</a></p>\n<h3>Because of a sense of shame</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:8\">GEN 3:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh5:8\">NEH 5:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:34\">MRK 9:34</a></p>\n<h3>When before a higher authority</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:19\">JDG 3:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:25\">MRK 1:25</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:35\">LUK 4:35</a></p>\n<h3>God's quiet voice</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:12-1Kgs19:13\">1KI 19:12–19:13</a></p>\n<h2>Absence of quietness</h2>\n<h3>Because of inner conflict</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job3:26\">JOB 3:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth3:18\">RUT 3:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job6:24\">JOB 6:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:21-Rom7:24\">ROM 7:21–7:24</a></p>\n<h3>Because of sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:20-Isa57:21\">ISA 57:20–57:21</a></strong></p>\n<h2>The quietness of God</h2>\n<h3>God chooses quietness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa18:4\">ISA 18:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job34:29\">JOB 34:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:14\">ISA 42:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:42\">EZK 16:42</a></p>\n<h3>God rejects quietness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa62:1\">ISA 62:1</a></strong></p>\n<h3>God brings quietness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps76:8\">PSA 76:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps46:10\">PSA 46:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps65:7\">PSA 65:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:9\">PSA 89:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:29\">PSA 107:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa24:8\">ISA 24:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:5\">ISA 25:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:17\">ZEP 3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:26\">MAT 8:26</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:39\">MRK 4:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:24\">LUK 8:24</a></p>\n<h2>Quietness before God</h2>\n<h3>Being quiet before God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:7\">PSA 37:7</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:15\">ISA 30:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:14\">EXO 14:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:26\">LAM 3:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:28\">1CO 14:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:34-1Cor14:35\">1CO 14:34–14:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev8:1\">REV 8:1</a></p>\n<h3>Quietness in prayer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:6\">MAT 6:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:4\">NEH 2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:46\">MRK 6:46</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:23\">MAT 14:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:16\">LUK 5:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:12\">LUK 6:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:18\">LUK 9:18</a></p>\n<h2>Quietness as calmness</h2>\n<h3>In contrast with the storm</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:26\">MAT 8:26</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:39\">MRK 4:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:24\">LUK 8:24</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:30\">PSA 107:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah1:11-Jonah1:15\">JON 1:11–1:15</a></p>\n<h3>In contrast with rashness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl10:4\">ECC 10:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:18\">PRO 15:18</a></p>\n<h3>In contrast with unrest</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa7:4\">ISA 7:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh8:11\">NEH 8:11</a></p>\n<h3>In contrast with anger</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:42\">EZK 16:42</a></strong></p>",
